{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":914,"text":"As a little girl, I always imagined"},{"time":3211,"text":"I would one day run away."},{"time":5546,"text":"From the age of six on,"},{"time":7010,"text":"I kept a packed bag with some clothes"},{"time":9462,"text":"and cans of food tucked away"},{"time":10988,"text":"in the back of a closet."},{"time":12982,"text":"There was a deep restlessness in me,"},{"time":15604,"text":"a primal fear that I would fall prey"},{"time":18150,"text":"to a life of routine and boredom."},{"time":20925,"text":"And so, many of my early memories involved"},{"time":23534,"text":"intricate daydreams where\nI would walk across borders,"},{"time":27100,"text":"forage for berries,"},{"time":28468,"text":"and meet all kinds of strange people"},{"time":30532,"text":"living unconventional lives on the road."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33576,"text":"Years have passed, but many of the adventures"},{"time":36160,"text":"I fantasized about as a child --"},{"time":38927,"text":"traveling and weaving my way"},{"time":40524,"text":"between worlds other than my own â€”"},{"time":42524,"text":"have become realities through my work"},{"time":44124,"text":"as a documentary photographer."},{"time":46685,"text":"But no other experience has felt as true"},{"time":49820,"text":"to my childhood dreams"},{"time":51740,"text":"as living amongst and documenting the lives"},{"time":54458,"text":"of fellow wanderers across the United States."},{"time":59150,"text":"This is the nomadic dream,"},{"time":61910,"text":"a different kind of American dream"},{"time":63820,"text":"lived by young hobos, travelers,"},{"time":66464,"text":"hitchhikers, vagrants and tramps."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69848,"text":"In most of our minds,"},{"time":71197,"text":"the vagabond is a creature from the past."},{"time":74288,"text":"The word \"hobo\" conjures up an old"},{"time":76591,"text":"black and white image"},{"time":78028,"text":"of a weathered old man covered in coal,"},{"time":80534,"text":"legs dangling out of a boxcar,"},{"time":82935,"text":"but these photographs are in color,"},{"time":85047,"text":"and they portray a community"},{"time":86830,"text":"swirling across the country,"},{"time":88552,"text":"fiercely alive and creatively free,"},{"time":91377,"text":"seeing sides of America that no one else"},{"time":93876,"text":"gets to see."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96066,"text":"Like their predecessors, today's nomads"},{"time":98756,"text":"travel the steel and asphalt arteries"},{"time":101423,"text":"of the United States."},{"time":103112,"text":"By day, they hop freight trains,\nstick out their thumbs,"},{"time":106300,"text":"and ride the highways with anyone"},{"time":108154,"text":"from truckers to soccer moms."},{"time":111170,"text":"By night, they sleep beneath the stars,"},{"time":113496,"text":"huddled together with their packs of dogs,"},{"time":116178,"text":"cats and pet rats between their bodies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119886,"text":"Some travelers take to the road by choice,"},{"time":122514,"text":"renouncing materialism, traditional jobs"},{"time":125100,"text":"and university degrees in exchange \nfor a glimmer of adventure."},{"time":129034,"text":"Others come from the underbelly of society,"},{"time":132284,"text":"never given a chance to mobilize upwards:"},{"time":135324,"text":"foster care dropouts, teenage runaways escaping"},{"time":138700,"text":"abuse and unforgiving homes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141844,"text":"Where others see stories of privation"},{"time":144754,"text":"and economic failure,"},{"time":146834,"text":"travelers view their own existence"},{"time":148694,"text":"through the prism of liberation and freedom."},{"time":152267,"text":"They'd rather live off of the excess"},{"time":154482,"text":"of what they view as a wasteful consumer society"},{"time":157432,"text":"than slave away at an unrealistic chance"},{"time":160233,"text":"at the traditional American dream."},{"time":162912,"text":"They take advantage of the fact"},{"time":165001,"text":"that in the United States,"},{"time":166549,"text":"up to 40 percent of all food ends up in the garbage"},{"time":170370,"text":"by scavenging for perfectly good produce"},{"time":173003,"text":"in dumpsters and trash cans."},{"time":175677,"text":"They sacrifice material comforts in exchange"},{"time":178046,"text":"for the space and the time to explore"},{"time":180769,"text":"a creative interior,"},{"time":182491,"text":"to dream, to read, to work on music, art and writing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187373,"text":"But there are many aspects to this life"},{"time":189881,"text":"that are far from idyllic."},{"time":192244,"text":"No one loses their inner demons"},{"time":194367,"text":"by taking to the road."},{"time":196076,"text":"Addiction is real, the elements are real,"},{"time":199238,"text":"freight trains maim and kill,"},{"time":201450,"text":"and anyone who has lived on the streets can attest"},{"time":204110,"text":"to the exhaustive list of laws"},{"time":206000,"text":"that criminalize homeless existence."},{"time":210106,"text":"Who here knows that in many cities"},{"time":211936,"text":"across the United States it is now illegal"},{"time":214586,"text":"to sit on the sidewalk,"},{"time":216619,"text":"to wrap oneself in a blanket,"},{"time":220006,"text":"to sleep in your own car,"},{"time":222741,"text":"to offer food to a stranger?"},{"time":226100,"text":"I know about these laws because I've watched"},{"time":227872,"text":"as friends and other travelers"},{"time":229664,"text":"were hauled off to jail or received citations"},{"time":232334,"text":"for committing these so-called crimes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235922,"text":"Many of you might be wondering why anyone"},{"time":238083,"text":"would choose a life like this,"},{"time":239794,"text":"under the thumb of discriminatory laws,"},{"time":242160,"text":"eating out of trash cans,"},{"time":243478,"text":"sleeping under bridges,"},{"time":245267,"text":"picking up seasonal jobs here and there."},{"time":248518,"text":"The answer to such a question is as varied"},{"time":251032,"text":"as the people that take to the road,"},{"time":253568,"text":"but travelers often respond with a single word:"},{"time":256950,"text":"freedom."},{"time":259281,"text":"Until we live in a society where every human"},{"time":262794,"text":"is assured dignity in their labor"},{"time":264863,"text":"so that they can work to live well,"},{"time":266738,"text":"not only work to survive,"},{"time":268845,"text":"there will always be an element of those"},{"time":270762,"text":"who seek the open road as a means of escape,"},{"time":273894,"text":"of liberation and, of course, of rebellion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278952,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":280968,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}